    "We test our GPT industrial bot operation in four use cases: an automatic parameter configuration system for a small factory in an I5.0 context, a faulty equipment discovery, a root cause analysis system, and a synthetic data generation tool.",
    "We train the GPT4-LM on various customized data from the experimental factory.",
    "We present the experimental results of the online and offline industrial bot versions.",
    "Figures 3 and 4 below show an overview of the online and offline industrial GPT bot we design before processing any query.",
